    "The manuscript, <em>Nachrichten von K\u00fcnstlern und Werkleuten</em> was completed three years before the first edition of <em>Le vite de pi\u00f9 eccellenti architetti, pittori, et scultori</em> by <a href=\"/vasarig\">Giorgio Vasari</a>.": [],
    "Though Neud\u00f6rfer did not intend it for publication as Vasari did, he remains the first German biographer of artists.": [
